name: Women's 'Gunner' Jacket (Sisters of EVE)
description: Advertise your stature as the terror of the celestial skies in this sleek, comfortable jacket. A solid black pillar rises in front and back to underline your undeniable and unyielding presence, while armbands and epaulettes of purest white on red give you the commanding appearance you deserve. Finally, the logo of the Sisters of EVE advertises your proud support for the only faction that matters.
